Category:Jedi Masters of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Jen Feyer was a Human Female Jedi Master stationed on Hoth during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire. While on Hoth she taught the skill of Artifice to Republic individuals.

Jen Feyer appears only in the game files for Star Wars: The Old Republic as her character was cut from the game. Jen Feyer's file can be found on Jedipedia. Although she was cut from the game Feyer's character is still visible in Aurek Base.
